        "content": "<p>The UpGrade Program was created in order to allow users who already own an AirVape device to buy their next one at a fraction of the retail price. Since we are continuously improving upon our products and releasing new models we want to make it far easier for customers to get a more advanced vaporizer, this means that every time you want to buy a higher-grade vape. You receive a 30% to 50% discount depending on the device you already own and the device you wish to have. The UpGrade program is available only for dry herb vaporizers and cannot be used for Oil/Concentrate vapes or accessories.<br/><br/>Choose the device you want to UpGrade from:</p>",
